snippet.title: One Day Builds: Time Management App Built in Flutter
snippet.description:
One Day Builds: Time Management App Built in Flutter

So this is my one day build, I built a time management app using the flutter framework.
It took me a total of 14hrs to get it done and if you want to check it out for yourself here is the link to the github repository:
https://github.com/KalleHallden/Time-management-app

This series on my channel is sort of an homage to Adam Savage's series on his channel called 'One day builds' which I highly recommend: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tUHJnl8qPM

CONTACT: halldenkalle@gmail.com

Computer: Macbook Pro - https://amzn.to/2GX54SU


Camera Gear:

Panasonic GH5 - https://amzn.to/2Nr09L2

MAIN LENS:  Lumix 12-35mm - https://amzn.to/2tzgJzp

DRONE: DJI Mavic Air - https://amzn.to/2NqkQa1

Secondary Lens: Panasonic 25mm - https://amzn.to/2UcTA1e

Secondary Lens: Olympus 45mm - https://amzn.to/2Ebp5SV

Zoom Lens: Panasonic 100-300mm - https://amzn.to/2U3UH3j

Monitor: AOC 27” - https://amzn.to/2U6hF9Z
